## 🌟 Inspiration

This project is inspired by **NVDA (NonVisual Desktop Access)**, a free and open-source screen reader that empowers blind and vision-impaired users to navigate the digital world. By simulating NVDA's behavior in a developer-friendly environment, we hope to create more inclusive web experiences.

